pe="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-1479_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Before delving deeper into the subject, let's define some key terms:</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-1481_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-1482_ pf-text-1"><b>Online training</b> - Educational courses or programs delivered over the internet, accessible remotely through computers or mobile devices.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-1484_ pf-text-1"><b>eLearning</b> - Electronic learning, which involves the use of digital technologies to deliver educational content and facilitate learning.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-1486_ pf-text-1"><b>Learning Management System (LMS)</b> - Software platform used to host, manage, and track online training courses and learning activities.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-1488_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1489_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-1490_ pf-heading-1-h3">Relevant legislation, regulations, and best practices</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_6438f104-d489-4558-bf1d-cd0988605f41.jpg?v=1709307481" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/3_6438f104-d489-4558-bf1d-cd0988605f41.jpg?v=1709307481 1536w" width="1600" height="1067" alt="Elevate Your Skills: Explore Accredited eLearning Courses - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Elevate Your Skills: Explore Accredited eLearning Courses - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3