ype="Paragraph3">Gone are the days of passive learning. Online training courses leverage interactive multimedia, simulations, and gamification techniques to engage learners and promote active participation. With features like discussion forums, virtual labs, and scenario-based learning, online courses create immersive learning experiences that foster knowledge retention and application.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-1549_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-1550_"><h1 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-1551_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h1><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_65fdc38b-896a-476f-a455-aeae69d0caac.jpg?v=1709198388" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_65fdc38b-896a-476f-a455-aeae69d0caac.jpg?v=1709198388 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Flexible Learning Options: Choose Your Path with UK Online Training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Flexible Learning Options: Choose Your Path with UK Online Training - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-fbyfCU cCdixN pf-1553_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-1554_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-1556_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-1557_ pf-text-1">According to a Chartered Institute of Personnel and Development (CIPD) report, 94% of UK employees believe that access to learning and development opportunities is crucial to their job satisfaction and performan